title: Hyper-V VHD
agents: windows
catalog: os/windows
license: GPL
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check provides information about VHDs configured on every virtual machine.

 In order to run, its needed to copy the hyperv_host.ps1 script to the plugin
 folder. The plugin sends data for all virutal machines as piggyback data in the 
 agent output of the Hyper-V host. 

item:
 Name of the VHD.

inventory:
 All VHDs found will be inventorized.

